      <title>欧洲央行行长金多斯称通胀数据正朝着正确方向发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/ecb-s-guindos-says-inflation-data-are-going-in-right-direction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行副行长路易斯·德金多斯表示，欧元区消费者价格数据给政策制定者带来了一些鼓励。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/ecb-s-guindos-says-inflation-data-are-going-in-right-direction</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 09:29:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚外汇储备因资金流入增加而创三年新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/-usd-kes-kenya-s-fx-reserves-hit-three-year-high-after-heightened-inflows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着资本加速流入东非国家肯尼亚，该国的外汇储备升至三年来的最高水平，有助于在其他新兴市场遭遇抛售的情况下保持其货币稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/-usd-kes-kenya-s-fx-reserves-hit-three-year-high-after-heightened-inflows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 09:17:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫伯罗特首席执行官对特朗普“相当放松”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-14/hapag-lloyd-ceo-fairly-relaxed-about-trump-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Hapag-Lloyd 首席执行官 Rolf Habben Jansen 表示，在下一届美国政府的领导下，对贸易商品的需求将“有所变动”，但“不会消失”。Jansen 预计特朗普第二任期内会出现“一些意外”，具体取决于关税政策的具体性质。Jansen 在“彭博社：开放贸易”节目中与 Kriti Gupta、Guy Johnson 和 Anna Edwards 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-14/hapag-lloyd-ceo-fairly-relaxed-about-trump-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 08:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
