      <title>日本大型银行提高利润目标并公布股票回购计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/mizuho-raises-profit-forecast-announces-share-buyback</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本最大的几家银行将年度利润预期上调至新高，并公布了回购股票的计划，以期从该国利率上升和股市繁荣中获得回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/mizuho-raises-profit-forecast-announces-share-buyback</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 06:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>锂价初现反弹，但长期前景黯淡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/lithium-in-nascent-recovery-but-longer-term-outlook-still-bleak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国电动汽车需求上升和供应减少，锂价正经历小幅复苏，但分析师警告称，2025 年这种电池金属仍可能出现过剩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-14/lithium-in-nascent-recovery-but-longer-term-outlook-still-bleak</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 05:43:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：等待更多数据，股市和美元小幅走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市周四上涨，受芯片设备制造商阿斯麦控股 (ASML Holding NV) 的乐观前景以及市场确信欧洲和美国央行将在 12 月进一步降息的提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 22:33:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国南部水务部门因水务行业困境而减少垃圾处理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/uk-s-southern-water-downgraded-to-junk-amid-water-sector-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[穆迪评级将南方水务有限公司 (Southern Water Ltd.) 的评级下调至垃圾级，并警告称，鉴于英国水务和污水处理供应商面临的困境以及该公司自身糟糕的业绩记录，其评级可能进一步下调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/uk-s-southern-water-downgraded-to-junk-amid-water-sector-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>OMV 称俄罗斯可能因仲裁结果胜诉而削减天然气供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/omv-wins-230-million-award-from-gazprom-on-2022-gas-dispute</link>
      <description><![CDATA[OMV AG 警告称，俄罗斯天然气供应可能中断，因为该公司打算停止向 Gazprom PJSC 支付进口费用，以收回其在仲裁中赢得的损失。欧洲期货飙升至一年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-13/omv-wins-230-million-award-from-gazprom-on-2022-gas-dispute</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Nov 2024 20:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
